ent\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant error_ratio and server_error_ratio observed, rising from 0.0 to 0.34, with median change ratio of 2.0.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error rate metrics (error_ratio, server_error_ratio) confirming unusual increase during anomaly period.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Error_ratio and server_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 0.32 with associated high median change ratio.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error metrics correlated with severe anomaly on this service instance.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Reduced max response time (rrt_max) dropped abnormally from 5330.0 to 1090.5, decline suggesting processing bottleneck.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Drastic 'rrt_max' drop at median and p99 observed.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "Based on the trace data analysis of the UUID `c9832b3e-191`, the following anomalies have been identified:\n\n### Detected Issues:\n\n#### Latency Spikes:\n1. `cartservice-2->redis`\n   - **Operation**: HMSET\n   - **Normal Avg Duration**: 1361.25 ms\n   - **Anomaly Avg Duration**: 8913.13 ms\n   - **Multiplier**: ~6.5x increase\n   - **Occurrences**: 1 instance\n\n2. `frontend-0->cartservice-2`\n   - **Operation**: POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart\n   - **Normal Avg Duration**: 2314.33 ms\n   - **Anomaly Avg Duration**: 10935.05 ms\n   - **Multiplier**: ~4.7x increase\n   - **Occurrences**: 1 instance\n\n3. `frontend-1->CurrencyService`\n   - **Operation**: hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies\n   - **Normal Avg Duration**: 2864.12 ms\n   - **Anomaly Avg Duration**: 5809.96 ms\n   - **Multiplier**: ~2.0x increase\n   - **Occurrences**: 1 instance\n\n4. `shippingservice-0->frontend-1`\n   - **Operation**: hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote\n   - **Normal Avg Duration**: 201.39 ms\n   - **Anomaly Avg Duration**: 390.00 ms\n   - **Multiplier**: ~1.94x increase\n   - **Oc